tasks.task: Assemble 7-piece gardening tool set from WorkPro.
subtasks: Unpack and organize transplanter with 4-inch depth engravings.
Prepare soil for planting using transplanter.
Dig holes with trowel for seedlings or plants.
Aerate and mix soil with hand fork.
Loosen and spread soil with cultivator.
Trim stems and small branches with pruning shears.
Arrange tools for easy access in storage tote.
